    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> miso paste</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>mayo</strong> and a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Mix until fully combined</p><p>Add<strong> half</strong> your<strong> soy sauce</strong> with <strong>half</strong> your <strong>rice vinegar</strong> (you'll use the rest later) and 1 tsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>cold water </strong>and stir it all together – this is your <strong>creamy miso dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1720168435139-x200.jpg",
