    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the rice is cooked and the green beans are tender, add the <strong>edamame beans</strong> to the pot with a generous pinch of<strong> salt</strong></p><p>Stir it all together and set aside (lid on) to steam until serving – this is your <strong>edamame rice</strong></p>",
