      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>edamame rice</strong>, topped with the <strong>soy basa</strong></p><p>Drizzle with the <strong>creamy miso dressing</strong> and top with the <strong>crispy onions</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
